text: Arthur Schmitt (27 November 1910 - 30 September 1989) was a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics, representing Saar. ==See also== * Saar at the 1952 Summer Olympics ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1989 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Saar Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Saarbrücken
